OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother mainly dry day with
OL,6,Fsome long spells of hot or very hot
OL,7,Fsunshine, although coasts a little
OL,8,Fcooler with onshore breezes
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Risk of the odd shower
OL,10,Fdeveloping later in the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA largely fine end to the day
OL,13,Fwith some late sunshine but an
OL,14,Fincreasing risk of showers overnight,
OL,15,Fperhaps occasionally heavy and
OL,16,Fthundery towards the end of the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
