OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,6,Fsome showery, perhaps thundery, rain
OL,7,Faround. Becoming brighter from the
OL,8,Fsouth through the afternoon but still
OL,9,Fsome showers around. A little cooler
OL,10,Fthan recently.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry,
OL,13,Fbright start Saturday but occasionally
OL,14,Fheavy rain spreads east in afternoon.
OL,15,FSunday and Monday look much cooler
OL,16,Fwith sunny spells and showers and an
OL,17,Foccasionally fresh southwesterly
OL,18,Fbreeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
